anach, wie das Phänomen als solches zustande kommt und was "interdisziplinär" bedeutet.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 20. Sep 2019) 4aDiscourse analysis. 4aDiskursanalyse. 70(DE-601)1042629660(DE-588)4074250-7aLinguistik2gnd 70(DE-601)1063176790(DE-588)4020535-6aGeschichtswissenschaft2gnd 70(DE-601)7351852390(DE-588)1030376883aKritische Diskursanalyse2gnd 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aKämper, Heidrun, eeditor.1 aWarnke, Ingo H., eeditor.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2015z9783110438710oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831103801320 cprintz978305006463540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783050065281423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783050065281.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DSPb2015